理\n\n### 保存 validate\n\n- [ ] validate error 阻断写盘\n- [ ] error 可定位到至少 card 级节点\n\n### 门禁\n\n- [ ] `npm run quality:studio` 全绿\n- [ ] docs/AI 已更新\n\n---\n\n## 6. 给批执行 Agent 的硬停语境\n\n命中以下应 `BLOCKED`：\n\n- 锚点仍仅 conf.participants 子集 / 双轨白名单\n- 新建卡不写 conf.cards 或不建 s-card.json\n- 删卡不删磁盘或 conf 不同步\n- conditionSummary 写盘替代 exit.condition 或保存一律 DEFAULT_CONDITION\n- critical 保存丢失\n- MOCK_ASSETS 仍作资源业务真源\n- validate 失败仍 PUT\n- 未迁移 golden_handoff 即删 doubao-sister 致 engine 红\n- Host beginCall 真跑 / 调试器真会话当作本批必达\n- `eslint-disable` / 门禁 allowlist 掩盖问题\n- 未授权改 `docs/人类/`\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":294,"fileSize":12906,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_需求.md","readRange":{"startLine":200,"endLine":294},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-4d4f2aa8-1440-4b16-88d1-d52e74b41ad1-12\nfc_288ee571-31b3-9221-a9f3-5436d65c7aad_5","startedAtMs":"1784721311199","completedAtMs":"1784721311342"},"model_call_id":"1923bc8e-c113-4e6e-8ac7-f8b8abda0a21-2-a8zf","session_id":"ce06a53c-3265-435a-baf5-df5c7cebef9f","timestamp_ms":1784721311372}
